## **🎨 Design Token Migration**

### **Color Tokens**

```css
/* ❌ Before */
.custom-button {
  @apply bg-blue-600 text-white;
}

/* ✅ After */
.custom-button {
  @apply bg-primary text-inverse;
}
```

### **Spacing Tokens**

```css
/* ❌ Before */
.card-padding {
  @apply px-4 py-3;
}

/* ✅ After - Use component variants */
<%= render DS::Card.new(size: "md") %>
```

## **🚀 Automation Tools**

### **Component Generator**

```bash
# Generate new DS component
rails generate ds_component Input variant:default,error size:sm,md,lg
```

### **Migration Scripts**

```ruby
# Script to find and suggest component replacements
class ComponentMigrationAnalyzer
  def analyze_view(file_path)
    content = File.read(file_path)
    suggestions = []
    
    # Find card patterns
    if content.match?(/bg-white.*border.*rounded/)
      suggestions << "Consider using DS::Card component"
    end
    
    # Find button patterns
    if content.match?(/bg-blue-.*text-white.*px-.*py-/)
      suggestions << "Consider using DS::Button component"
    end
    
    suggestions
  end
end
```

